#: .\templates\pages\about.html:25
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    General Food Industry Co., Ltd. (GFI) is a Bangkok-based "
"company specialising in the import, export, and distribution of food "
"additives and ingredients. We serve food and beverage manufacturers, "
"processors, and producers throughout Thailand and across Southeast Asia.\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""

#: .\templates\pages\about.html:30
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    Founded on a commitment to quality and traceability, GFI "
"works directly with certified global suppliers to ensure every product we "
"handle meets the highest food safety standards. Our team combines deep "
"product knowledge with strong logistics capabilities to deliver reliable "
"supply chain solutions.\n"
"                    "
msgstr ""

#: .\templates\pages\about.html:35
msgid ""
"\n"
"                    We believe in building lasting partnerships — "
"understanding our customers' formulation needs and supporting them with "
"consistent supply, technical guidance, and responsive service.\n"
"                    "
